org.polarsys.chess.core.profiles

Class MARTEProfileManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.polarsys.chess.core.profiles.MARTEProfileManager

  • public class MARTEProfileManager
extends java.lang.Object
    This class wraps the MARTE profile resource and is used for loading the profile and applying its stereotypes.
    Author:
    Alessandro Zovi
